GIT WORKFLOW (MANDATORY AFTER EACH SECTION)

After completing each section, ALWAYS follow this workflow:

Create feature branch
feature/XX-section-name
(example: feature/05-rag-systems)

Stage all changes
git add .

Commit with descriptive message
[AI-Learning-Lab] Complete section XX – <section-name>

Push feature branch
git push -u origin feature/XX-section-name

Switch to main
git checkout main

Merge feature branch
git merge feature/XX-section-name

Push main
git push origin main

Never skip this workflow

Clean git history is mandatory

AI BEHAVIOR OVERRIDES (VERY IMPORTANT)

